p: A BDI value of 0 indicates an effect similar to ethanol, while any value greater than 0 indicates biting deterrent effect relative to ethanol. BDI values not significantly different from 1, are statistically similar to DEET. BDI values were analyzed using SAS Proc ANOVA [ 31]. To determine whether confidence intervals include the values of 0 or 1 for treatments, Scheffeâ€™s multiple comparison procedure with the option of CLM was used in SAS [ 31]. LC 50 values for larvicidal data were calculated by using SAS, Proc Probit [ 31].
